{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882517995,"sessionID":"ses_2852778a9ffeIT20W4PZTyOUe6","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad8b9cc001LNTGdEciQt1d6K","messageID":"msg_d7ad8af25001Jay1msJBgRNTGZ","sessionID":"ses_2852778a9ffeIT20W4PZTyOUe6","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_85febc2a180b423b9d69bcb7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n2: \n3: **Module:** client-go\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** L\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube 项目生成标准的 Kubernetes 风格 Go 客户端库（`client-go`），提供对自定义资源 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter`（API Group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`）的类型安全 CRUD 操作、事件监听（Informer）和缓存索引（Lister）能力。\n10: \n11: 该客户端库遵循 `k8s.io/code-generator` 的约定，使 AgentCube 的 Go 用户能够以与原生 Kubernetes 客户端一致的方式操作自定义资源，同时为 AgentCube 内部控制器和 Operator 提供基础的客户端基础设施。\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: ### In Scope\n16: \n17: 1. **Clientset 顶层入口**\n18:    - `Interface` / `Clientset` 结构体及构造函数（`NewForConfig`, `NewForConfigAndClient`, `NewForConfigOrDie`, `New`）\n19:    - `Discovery()` 和 `RuntimeV1alpha1()` 分组访问器\n20: \n21: 2. **Typed Client — `runtime/v1alpha1`**\n22:    - `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` / `RuntimeV1alpha1Client`（REST 客户端，`APIPath=/apis`）\n23:    - `AgentRuntimeInterface` — `AgentRuntime` 资源的完整 CRUD + Watch + Patch + DeleteCollection\n24:    - `CodeInterpreterInterface` — `CodeInterpreter` 资源的完整 CRUD + Watch + Patch + DeleteCollection\n25:    - `AgentRuntimeExpansion` / `CodeInterpreterExpansion` 空接口（预留自定义方法）\n26:    - Fake typed clients（`fake_runtime_client.go`, `fake_agentruntime.go`, `fake_codeinterpreter.go`）\n27: \n28: 3. **Scheme 注册**\n29:    - `register.go` — 构建 `Scheme`, `Codecs`, `ParameterCodec`；`AddToScheme` 注册 `runtime/v1alpha1` 类型\n30: \n31: 4. **Informer Factory**\n32:    - `SharedInformerFactory` — `Start`/`Shutdown`/`WaitForCacheSync`/`ForResource`/`InformerFor`\n33:    - 构造函数：`NewSharedInformerFactory`, `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions`\n34:    - Options：`WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`\n35:    - Group/Version 访问器链：`Runtime()` → `V1alpha1()` → `AgentRuntimes()`/`CodeInterpreters()`\n36:    - Per-type Informer：`AgentRuntimeInformer`, `CodeInterpreterInformer`（含 `Informer()` + `Lister()`）\n37:    - Generic `ForResource` 路由（`agentruntimes` / `codeinterpreters`）\n38: \n39: 5. **Listers**\n40:    - `AgentRuntimeLister` / `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` — 基于本地缓存的只读索引\n41:    - `CodeInterpreterLister` / `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister`\n42:    - Expansion 空接口（四个类型）\n43: \n44: 6. **Fake Clientset**\n45:    - `NewSimpleClientset` / `NewClientset` — 内存级 Fake Clientset\n46:    - Scheme 注册 wiring\n47: \n48: 7. **代码生成管线**\n49:    - `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n50:    - 使用 `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1，`--with-watch` 标志\n51:    - 输出包路径：`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n52: \n53: ### Out of Scope\n54: \n55: - 手写客户端逻辑（所有代码由 code-generator 自动生成）\n56: - API Server 端逻辑（CRD 定义、控制器、Webhook）\n57: - 认证/授权配置（由调用方通过 `rest.Config` 提供）\n58: - 自定义 Informer/Lister 扩展方法（Expansion 接口为空，由消费者自行实现）\n59: - 多 API Group 或未来版本的客户端生成（当前仅 `runtime/v1alpha1`）\n60: \n61: ## Architecture Summary\n62: \n63: ### Current State\n64: \n65: AgentCube 定义了 CRD 类型 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter`（`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`），但尚未生成对应的 Kubernetes 风格客户端库。Go 消费者需要手动构造 REST 请求或使用通用 `dynamic.Client`，缺乏类型安全和 Informer/Lister 模式支持。\n66: \n67: ### Target State\n68: \n69: 生成完整的 `client-go` 模块，包含四层架构：\n70: \n71: ```\n72: Clientset (顶层入口)\n73:   └── RuntimeV1alpha1Client (分组 REST 客户端)\n74:         ├── AgentRuntimeInterface (typed REST)\n75:         └── CodeInterpreterInterface (typed REST)\n76: \n77: SharedInformerFactory (事件驱动)\n78:   └── Runtime().V1alpha1()\n79:         ├── AgentRuntimeInformer → AgentRuntimeLister\n80:         └── CodeInterpreterInformer → CodeInterpreterLister\n81: \n82: FakeClientset (测试替身)\n83:   └── 实现全部 Interface，内存存储\n84: ```\n85: \n86: 所有代码由 `k8s.io/code-generator` 从 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 的类型定义自动生成，通过 `// +genclient` 等 marker 控制生成行为。\n87: \n88: ## Impact Analysis\n89: \n90: ### 依赖影响\n91: \n92: | 影响项 | 说明 |\n93: |--------|------|\n94: | **新增模块** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` 作为独立 Go module 或子包 |\n95: | **传递依赖** | `k8s.io/client-go`, `k8s.io/apimachinery` (v0.34.1), `k8s.io/code-generator` (dev-only) |\n96: | **Go 版本** | 需与 code-generator v0.34.1 兼容（Go 1.22+） |\n97: | **构建系统** | `Makefile` 新增 `gen-client` target；`hack/update-codegen.sh` 脚本 |\n98: \n99: ### 消费者影响\n100: \n101: - **正向**：提供类型安全的客户端，消除手动构造 REST 请求的样板代码\n102: - **正向**：Informer + Lister 模式支持高效的本地缓存和事件驱动编程\n103: - **正向**：Fake clients 使单元测试无需真实集群\n104: - **风险**：API 类型定义变更后需重新生成客户端（通过 `make gen-client` 自动化缓解）\n105: - **向后兼容**：生成代码的接口签名由 CRD 类型决定；类型字段变更可能导致消费者编译失败\n106: \n107: ### 安全影响\n108: \n109: - 客户端本身不处理认证/授权，依赖调用方提供正确的 `rest.Config`（含 token/cert）\n110: - Fake clients 仅用于测试，不涉及生产数据\n111: \n112: ### 性能影响\n113: \n114: - Informer 全量 List 后 Watch 增量更新，初始同步时间与资源数量成正比\n115: - Lister 基于 `cache.Indexer`，读操作 O(1)（按 key）或 O(n)（按 selector 遍历）\n116: - 生成代码本身无性能开销，与手写等效\n117: \n118: ### 运维影响\n119: \n120: - 生成代码不应手动修改（`Expansion` 接口除外）\n121: - CRD 类型变更后需执行 `make gen-client` 重新生成并提交 diff\n122: - 生成的文件量较大（~20 个文件），但全部为确定性输出\n123: \n124: ## Alternatives Considered\n125: \n126: ### 1. 手写 REST 客户端（❌ 不采用）\n127: \n128: **做法**：手动实现 `AgentRuntimeClient` 和 `CodeInterpreterClient`，使用 `rest.RESTClient` 发送请求。\n129: \n130: **优点**：无外部生成工具依赖，可完全定制\n131: \n132: **缺点**：\n133: - 大量样板代码（CRUD + Watch + Patch + Options 构造）\n134: - 易出错，类型安全难以保证\n135: - 需自行实现 Informer/Lister 模式（复杂度高）\n136: - 与 Kubernetes 生态不一致，增加学习成本\n137: \n138: **决策**：不采用。维护成本过高，无法利用成熟的 code-generator 生态。\n139: \n140: ### 2. 使用 controller-runtime 的 `client.Client`（❌ 不采用）\n141: \n142: **做法**：依赖 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client` 提供通用客户端。\n143: \n144: **优点**：更高层抽象，内置缓存和索引，与控制器框架集成紧密\n145: \n146: **缺点**：\n147: - 引入完整的 controller-runtime 依赖（较重，含 manager、reconcile 等）\n148: - 不适合仅需轻量客户端的场景（如独立 CLI 工具）\n149: - 动态类型（`client.Object`）不如生成代码的类型安全\n150: \n151: **决策**：不采用。AgentCube 的部分消费者可能只需要轻量客户端而非完整控制器框架。controller-runtime 可作为上层可选依赖。\n152: \n153: ### 3. 使用 dynamic.Client + unstructured（❌ 不采用）\n154: \n155: **做法**：使用 `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic` 操作 `unstructured.Unstructured` 对象。\n156: \n157: **优点**：无需生成代码，支持任意 CRD\n158: \n159: **缺点**：\n160: - 无编译时类型检查，字段访问通过 map 操作\n161: - 代码冗长且易出错（`obj.Object[\"spec\"].(map[string]interface{})[\"replicas\"]`）\n162: - 无 Informer/Lister 的类型安全变体\n163: \n164: **决策**：不采用。类型安全性是核心需求。\n165: \n166: ### 4. k8s.io/code-generator 生成（✅ 选定方案）\n167: \n168: **做法**：使用 Kubernetes 官方 `code-generator` 工具从 `pkg/apis/` 类型定义生成客户端。\n169: \n170: **优点**：\n171: - Kubernetes 官方标准，与生态完全一致\n172: - 自动生成 Clientset、Informer、Lister、Fake 完整工具链\n173: - 编译时类型安全\n174: - 社区成熟，长期维护有保障\n175: - 与现有 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 类型定义无缝集成\n176: \n177: **缺点**：\n178: - 生成代码量大（~20 个文件）\n179: - 需维护 code-generator 版本和生成脚本\n180: - CRD 类型变更后需重新生成\n181: \n182: **决策**：采用。符合 Kubernetes 生态最佳实践，长期维护成本最低。\n183: \n184: ## Upstream Dependencies\n185: \n186: | 依赖 | 版本 | 用途 |\n187: |------|------|------|\n188: | `k8s.io/code-generator` | v0.34.1 | 代码生成工具（dev-only） |\n189: | `k8s.io/client-go` | v0.34.1 | REST 客户端、Discovery、Fake 基础 |\n190: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.34.1 | Scheme、Codec、meta 类型 |\n191: | AgentCube `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | 本地 | CRD 类型定义（生成输入） |\n192: \n193: ### 类型定义前置条件\n194: \n195: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 需包含：\n196: - `AgentRuntime` / `AgentRuntimeList` 结构体及 `// +genclient` marker\n197: - `CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList` 结构体及 `// +genclient` marker\n198: - `SchemeBuilder` / `AddToScheme` 注册\n199: - DeepCopy 方法（由 `deepcopy-gen` 预先生成）\n200: \n201: ## Status\n202: \n203: - [ ] Proposal review\n204: - [ ] Implementation\n205: - [ ] Verification\n\n(End of file - total 205 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n**Module:** client-go\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** L\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 项目生成标准的 Kubernetes 风格 Go 客户端库（`client-go`），提供对自定义资源 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter`（API Group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`）的类型安全 CRUD 操作、事件监听（Informer）和缓存索引（Lister）能力。\n\n该客户端库遵循 `k8s.io/code-generator` 的约定，使 AgentCube 的 Go 用户能够以与原生 Kubernetes 客户端一致的方式操作自定义资源，同时为 AgentCube 内部控制器和 Operator 提供基础的客户端基础设施。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **Clientset 顶层入口**\n   - `Interface` / `Clientset` 结构体及构造函数（`NewForConfig`, `NewForConfigAndClient`, `NewForConfigOrDie`, `New`）\n   - `Discovery()` 和 `RuntimeV1alpha1()` 分组访问器\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882517973,"end":1775882517993}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882519201,"sessionID":"ses_2852778a9ffeIT20W4PZTyOUe6","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad8be5a001wEivUEXnqPNvbK","messageID":"msg_d7ad8af25001Jay1msJBgRNTGZ","sessionID":"ses_2852778a9ffeIT20W4PZTyOUe6","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_2f11d854c423489bb75046ff","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `client-go`\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** L\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n9: \n10: ## Scope\n11: \n12: This delta spec covers the generated Kubernetes client-go library for API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, module path `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`. It SHALL provide a typed Clientset, per-resource REST clients, SharedInformerFactory, Listers, and in-memory Fake clients for the `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` custom resources. All code SHALL be generated via `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh` using `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 with `--with-watch` flag.\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Clientset\n17: \n18: ### Requirement: Interface contract\n19: \n20: The system SHALL provide a `Clientset` implementing `Interface` with discovery and group accessor methods.\n21: \n22: #### Scenario: Interface exposes Discovery and RuntimeV1alpha1\n23: - **GIVEN** the `Interface` type is defined in `clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n24: - **WHEN** the interface is inspected\n25: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface` and `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: Clientset struct embeds DiscoveryClient\n28: - **GIVEN** the `Clientset` struct is defined\n29: - **WHEN** the struct fields are inspected\n30: - **THEN** it SHALL embed `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and hold `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`\n31: \n32: ### Requirement: Clientset constructors\n33: \n34: The system SHALL provide four constructor functions for creating `Clientset` instances.\n35: \n36: #### Scenario: NewForConfig creates clientset from rest.Config\n37: - **GIVEN** a valid `*rest.Config` pointing to a Kubernetes API server\n38: - **WHEN** `NewForConfig(c)` is called\n39: - **THEN** it SHALL return `(*Clientset, nil)` with all group clients initialized, or `(*Clientset, error)` on failure\n40: \n41: #### Scenario: NewForConfigAndClient uses custom http.Client\n42: - **GIVEN** a valid `*rest.Config` and `*http.Client`\n43: - **WHEN** `NewForConfigAndClient(c, httpClient)` is called\n44: - **THEN** it SHALL return a `*Clientset` using the provided HTTP client for transport\n45: \n46: #### Scenario: NewForConfigOrDie panics on invalid config\n47: - **GIVEN** an invalid `*rest.Config` (e.g., malformed host)\n48: - **WHEN** `NewForConfigOrDie(c)` is called\n49: - **THEN** it SHALL panic\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: NewForConfigOrDie succeeds with valid config\n52: - **GIVEN** a valid `*rest.Config`\n53: - **WHEN** `NewForConfigOrDie(c)` is called\n54: - **THEN** it SHALL return a `*Clientset` without panicking\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: New creates clientset from rest.Interface\n57: - **GIVEN** a pre-configured `rest.Interface`\n58: - **WHEN** `New(restInterface)` is called\n59: - **THEN** it SHALL return a `*Clientset` with the typed client wired to the provided interface\n60: \n61: ### Requirement: RuntimeV1alpha1 group accessor\n62: \n63: The system SHALL provide access to the `runtime/v1alpha1` API group client.\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: RuntimeV1alpha1 returns typed group client\n66: - **GIVEN** a `Clientset` instance\n67: - **WHEN** `cs.RuntimeV1alpha1()` is called\n68: - **THEN** it SHALL return a `runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n69: \n70: ---\n71: \n72: ## Typed Client — runtime/v1alpha1\n73: \n74: ### Requirement: RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n75: \n76: The system SHALL provide a group-level interface exposing REST client and resource getters.\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: RuntimeV1alpha1Interface contract\n79: - **GIVEN** the `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` is defined in `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n80: - **WHEN** the interface is inspected\n81: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `RESTClient() rest.Interface`, `AgentRuntimesGetter`, and `CodeInterpretersGetter`\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: RuntimeV1alpha1Client implements the interface\n84: - **GIVEN** the `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` struct\n85: - **WHEN** its methods are inspected\n86: - **THEN** it SHALL implement all methods of `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n87: \n88: #### Scenario: REST defaults are configured correctly\n89: - **GIVEN** a `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` instance\n90: - **WHEN** its REST client is inspected\n91: - **THEN** `GroupVersion` SHALL be `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion`, `APIPath` SHALL be `/apis`, and negotiated serializer SHALL come from `clientset/versioned/scheme`\n92: \n93: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime typed client\n94: \n95: The system SHALL provide a typed REST client for the `agentruntimes` resource.\n96: \n97: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimesGetter interface\n98: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimesGetter` interface\n99: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n100: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface`\n101: \n102: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — Create\n103: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface` and a valid `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`\n104: - **WHEN** `Create(ctx, agentRuntime, opts)` is called\n105: - **THEN** it SHALL POST to `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes` and return the created object\n106: \n107: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — Update\n108: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface` and an existing `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`\n109: - **WHEN** `Update(ctx, agentRuntime, opts)` is called\n110: - **THEN** it SHALL PUT to the resource URL and return the updated object\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — UpdateStatus\n113: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface` and an `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime` with modified status\n114: - **WHEN** `UpdateStatus(ctx, agentRuntime, opts)` is called\n115: - **THEN** it SHALL PUT to the `/status` subresource endpoint\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — Get\n118: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface` and a resource name\n119: - **WHEN** `Get(ctx, name, opts)` is called\n120: - **THEN** it SHALL GET the resource and return `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`\n121: \n122: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — List\n123: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface`\n124: - **WHEN** `List(ctx, opts)` is called\n125: - **THEN** it SHALL GET the collection and return `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList`\n126: \n127: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — Delete\n128: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface` and a resource name\n129: - **WHEN** `Delete(ctx, name, opts)` is called\n130: - **THEN** it SHALL DELETE the resource and return `nil` on success or `error` on failure\n131: \n132: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — DeleteCollection\n133: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface`\n134: - **WHEN** `DeleteCollection(ctx, deleteOpts, listOpts)` is called\n135: - **THEN** it SHALL DELETE all resources matching `listOpts`\n136: \n137: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — Watch\n138: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface`\n139: - **WHEN** `Watch(ctx, opts)` is called\n140: - **THEN** it SHALL establish a watch stream and return `watch.Interface`\n141: \n142: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInterface CRUD — Patch\n143: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntimeInterface`, name, patch type, and patch data\n144: - **WHEN** `Patch(ctx, name, pt, data, opts, subresources...)` is called\n145: - **THEN** it SHALL PATCH the resource and return the patched `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`\n146: \n147: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime resource plural\n148: - **GIVEN** the AgentRuntime REST client\n149: - **WHEN** the resource path is constructed\n150: - **THEN** the plural form SHALL be `agentruntimes`\n151: \n152: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreter typed client\n153: \n154: The system SHALL provide a typed REST client for the `codeinterpreters` resource with the same method shape as AgentRuntime.\n155: \n156: #### Scenario: CodeInterpretersGetter interface\n157: - **GIVEN** the `CodeInterpretersGetter` interface\n158: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n159: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface`\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterInterface methods\n162: - **GIVEN** the `CodeInterpreterInterface`\n163: - **WHEN** its methods are inspected\n164: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `DeleteCollection`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch` with types `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList`\n165: \n166: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter resource plural\n167: - **GIVEN** the CodeInterpreter REST client\n168: - **WHEN** the resource path is constructed\n169: - **THEN** the plural form SHALL be `codeinterpreters`\n170: \n171: ### Requirement: Expansion hooks\n172: \n173: The system SHALL provide empty expansion interfaces for custom method injection.\n174: \n175: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeExpansion interface\n176: - **GIVEN** `generated_expansion.go`\n177: - **WHEN** `AgentRuntimeExpansion` is inspected\n178: - **THEN** it SHALL be an empty interface `interface{}`\n179: \n180: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterExpansion interface\n181: - **GIVEN** `generated_expansion.go`\n182: - **WHEN** `CodeInterpreterExpansion` is inspected\n183: - **THEN** it SHALL be an empty interface `interface{}`\n184: \n185: ---\n186: \n187: ## Scheme\n188: \n189: ### Requirement: Scheme registration\n190: \n191: The system SHALL register all `runtime/v1alpha1` types with a shared `Scheme`, `Codecs`, and `ParameterCodec`.\n192: \n193: #### Scenario: register.go builds Scheme\n194: - **GIVEN** `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n195: - **WHEN** the package is loaded\n196: - **THEN** `Scheme`, `Codecs`, and `ParameterCodec` SHALL be initialized as package-level variables\n197: \n198: #### Scenario: AddToScheme registers v1alpha1 types\n199: - **GIVEN** `AddToScheme` is called on a `*runtime.Scheme`\n200: - **WHEN** registration completes\n201: - **THEN** all `runtime/v1alpha1` types (AgentRuntime, AgentRuntimeList, CodeInterpreter, CodeInterpreterList) SHALL be registered\n202: \n203: ---\n204: \n205: ## Informer Factory\n206: \n207: ### Requirement: SharedInformerFactory interface\n208: \n209: The system SHALL provide a shared informer factory for cache-based event distribution.\n210: \n211: #### Scenario: SharedInformerFactory contract\n212: - **GIVEN** the `SharedInformerFactory` interface in `informers/externalversions/factory.go`\n213: - **WHEN** the interface is inspected\n214: - **THEN** it SHALL embed `internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory` and declare `Start`, `Shutdown`, `WaitForCacheSync`, `ForResource`, `InformerFor`, and `Runtime()` methods\n215: \n216: #### Scenario: NewSharedInformerFactory constructor\n217: - **GIVEN** a `versioned.Interface` client and `defaultResync time.Duration`\n218: - **WHEN** `NewSharedInformerFactory(client, defaultResync)` is called\n219: - **THEN** it SHALL return a `SharedInformerFactory` with the provided resync interval\n220: \n221: #### Scenario: NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions\n222: - **GIVEN** a client, resync duration, and options (`WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`)\n223: - **WHEN** `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(client, defaultResync, options...)` is called\n224: - **THEN** it SHALL return a configured `SharedInformerFactory` applying all provided options\n225: \n226: ### Requirement: Start/Shutdown/WaitForCacheSync lifecycle\n227: \n228: The system SHALL manage informer lifecycle through start, shutdown, and cache sync operations.\n229: \n230: #### Scenario: Start begins informer goroutines\n231: - **GIVEN** a `SharedInformerFactory` with registered informers\n232: - **WHEN** `Start(stopCh)` is called\n233: - **THEN** all registered informers SHALL begin watching their resources until `stopCh` is closed\n234: \n235: #### Scenario: Shutdown stops all informers\n236: - **GIVEN** a running `SharedInformerFactory`\n237: - **WHEN** `Shutdown()` is called\n238: - **THEN** all informers SHALL be stopped and resources released\n239: \n240: #### Scenario: WaitForCacheSync blocks until caches are ready\n241: - **GIVEN** a `SharedInformerFactory` with started informers\n242: - **WHEN** `WaitForCacheSync(stopCh)` is called\n243: - **THEN** it SHALL block until all informers have synced their caches or `stopCh` is closed, returning a `map[reflect.Type]bool`\n244: \n245: ### Requirement: Group and version accessors\n246: \n247: The system SHALL provide hierarchical accessors for group → version → informer navigation.\n248: \n249: #### Scenario: Runtime() returns group interface\n250: - **GIVEN** a `SharedInformerFactory`\n251: - **WHEN** `factory.Runtime()` is called\n252: - **THEN** it SHALL return `externalversionsruntime.Interface`\n253: \n254: #### Scenario: V1alpha1() returns version interface\n255: - **GIVEN** a group `Interface`\n256: - **WHEN** `group.V1alpha1()` is called\n257: - **THEN** it SHALL return `v1alpha1.Interface` with `AgentRuntimes()` and `CodeInterpreters()` accessors\n258: \n259: ### Requirement: Per-type informers\n260: \n261: The system SHALL provide informer and lister access for each resource type.\n262: \n263: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeInformer interface\n264: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeInformer` interface\n265: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n266: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister`\n267: \n268: #### Scenario: NewAgentRuntimeInformer constructor\n269: - **GIVEN** a `versioned.Interface` client and `resync time.Duration`\n270: - **WHEN** `NewAgentRuntimeInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers)` is called\n271: - **THEN** it SHALL return a `cache.SharedIndexInformer` watching AgentRuntime resources\n272: \n273: #### Scenario: NewFilteredAgentRuntimeInformer\n274: - **GIVEN** a client, namespace, resync, indexers, and `tweakListOptions`\n275: - **WHEN** `NewFilteredAgentRuntimeInformer` is called\n276: - **THEN** it SHALL return an informer with list options modified by `tweakListOptions`\n277: \n278: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterInformer mirrors AgentRuntimeInformer\n279: - **GIVEN** the `CodeInterpreterInformer` interface\n280: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n281: - **THEN** it SHALL declare the same methods as `AgentRuntimeInformer` but returning `CodeInterpreterLister`\n282: \n283: ### Requirement: Generic resource routing\n284: \n285: The system SHALL route GVR lookups to the correct typed informer.\n286: \n287: #### Scenario: ForResource routes agentruntimes\n288: - **GIVEN** `ForResource(v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"agentruntimes\"))`\n289: - **WHEN** the method is called\n290: - **THEN** it SHALL return `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()` wrapped in a `GenericInformer`\n291: \n292: #### Scenario: ForResource routes codeinterpreters\n293: - **GIVEN** `ForResource(v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"codeinterpreters\"))`\n294: - **WHEN** the method is called\n295: - **THEN** it SHALL return `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters().Informer()` wrapped in a `GenericInformer`\n296: \n297: #### Scenario: ForResource returns error for unknown resource\n298: - **GIVEN** `ForResource` with an unrecognized GVR\n299: - **WHEN** the method is called\n300: - **THEN** it SHALL return `(nil, error)`\n301: \n302: ### Requirement: internalinterfaces\n303: \n304: The system SHALL define base factory interfaces for informer construction.\n305: \n306: #### Scenario: NewInformerFunc signature\n307: - **GIVEN** the `internalinterfaces` package\n308: - **WHEN** `NewInformerFunc` is inspected\n309: - **THEN** it SHALL be `func(versioned.Interface, time.Duration) cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n310: \n311: #### Scenario: internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory\n312: - **GIVEN** the `internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory` interface\n313: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n314: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `Start(stopCh <-chan struct{})` and `InformerFor(obj runtime.Object, newFunc NewInformerFunc) cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n315: \n316: #### Scenario: TweakListOptionsFunc\n317: - **GIVEN** the `TweakListOptionsFunc` type\n318: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n319: - **THEN** it SHALL be `func(*metav1.ListOptions)`\n320: \n321: ---\n322: \n323: ## Listers\n324: \n325: ### Requirement: AgentRuntimeLister\n326: \n327: The system SHALL provide a read-only caching layer for AgentRuntime objects.\n328: \n329: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeLister interface\n330: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeLister` interface in `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n331: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n332: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)`, `AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister`, and `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion`\n333: \n334: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface\n335: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` interface\n336: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n337: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)`, `Get(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)`, and `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion`\n338: \n339: #### Scenario: NewAgentRuntimeLister uses correct GroupResource\n340: - **GIVEN** `NewAgentRuntimeLister(indexer cache.Indexer)` is called\n341: - **WHEN** the lister is created\n342: - **THEN** it SHALL use `runtimev1alpha1.Resource(\"agentruntime\").GroupResource()` for error reporting\n343: \n344: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterLister\n345: \n346: The system SHALL provide a read-only caching layer for CodeInterpreter objects with the same pattern.\n347: \n348: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterLister interface\n349: - **GIVEN** the `CodeInterpreterLister` interface\n350: - **WHEN** it is inspected\n351: - **THEN** it SHALL declare `List`, `CodeInterpreters(namespace) CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister`, and `CodeInterpreterListerExpansion`\n352: \n353: #### Scenario: NewCodeInterpreterLister uses correct GroupResource\n354: - **GIVEN** `NewCodeInterpreterLister(indexer)` is called\n355: - **WHEN** the lister is created\n356: - **THEN** it SHALL use `Resource(\"codeinterpreter\").GroupResource()`\n357: \n358: ### Requirement: Lister expansion interfaces\n359: \n360: The system SHALL provide empty expansion interfaces for all lister types.\n361: \n362: #### Scenario: All four expansion interfaces are empty\n363: - **GIVEN** `expansion_generated.go`\n364: - **WHEN** the file is inspected\n365: - **THEN** `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion`, `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion`, `CodeInterpreterListerExpansion`, and `CodeInterpreterNamespaceListerExpansion` SHALL all be empty interfaces\n366: \n367: ---\n368: \n369: ## Fake Clients\n370: \n371: ### Requirement: Fake typed clients\n372: \n373: The system SHALL provide in-memory fake implementations of typed interfaces for testing.\n374: \n375: #### Scenario: Fake runtime group client\n376: - **GIVEN** `fake/fake_runtime_client.go`\n377: - **WHEN** the `FakeRuntimeV1alpha1` struct is inspected\n378: - **THEN** it SHALL implement `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` and embed `*testing.Fake`\n379: \n380: #### Scenario: Fake AgentRuntime client\n381: - **GIVEN** `fake/fake_agentruntime.go`\n382: - **WHEN** the fake AgentRuntime client is inspected\n383: - **THEN** it SHALL implement `AgentRuntimeInterface` using `*testing.Fake` actions\n384: \n385: #### Scenario: Fake CodeInterpreter client\n386: - **GIVEN** `fake/fake_codeinterpreter.go`\n387: - **WHEN** the fake CodeInterpreter client is inspected\n388: - **THEN** it SHALL implement `CodeInterpreterInterface` using `*testing.Fake` actions\n389: \n390: ### Requirement: Fake clientset\n391: \n392: The system SHALL provide a fake `Clientset` for integration testing without a real API server.\n393: \n394: #### Scenario: NewSimpleClientset creates fake clientset with objects\n395: - **GIVEN** `fake.NewSimpleClientset(objects...)` is called with initial runtime objects\n396: - **WHEN** the fake clientset is returned\n397: - **THEN** it SHALL contain the provided objects in its tracker and implement `versioned.Interface`\n398: \n399: #### Scenario: NewClientset creates fake clientset with custom reactor\n400: - **GIVEN** `fake.NewClientset(client, objects...)` is called\n401: - **WHEN** the fake clientset is returned\n402: - **THEN** it SHALL use the provided `*restclient.RESTClient` and tracker\n403: \n404: #### Scenario: Fake clientset Scheme registration\n405: - **GIVEN** `fake/register.go`\n406: - **WHEN** the package is loaded\n407: - **THEN** it SHALL wire the same scheme as the real clientset for type recognition\n408: \n409: ---\n410: \n411: ## Regeneration\n412: \n413: ### Requirement: make gen-client target\n414: \n415: The system SHALL provide a Makefile target to regenerate all client-go code.\n416: \n417: #### Scenario: make gen-client runs update-codegen.sh\n418: - **GIVEN** the Makefile defines `gen-client`\n419: - **WHEN** `make gen-client` is executed\n420: - **THEN** it SHALL invoke `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n421: \n422: #### Scenario: update-codegen.sh uses correct code-generator version\n423: - **GIVEN** `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n424: - **WHEN** the script is inspected\n425: - **THEN** it SHALL use `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1\n426: \n427: #### Scenario: code-generator flags include --with-watch\n428: - **GIVEN** the code-generator invocation in `update-codegen.sh`\n429: - **WHEN** the command is inspected\n430: - **THEN** it SHALL include `--with-watch` flag for watch support\n431: \n432: #### Scenario: output package is correct\n433: - **GIVEN** the code-generator invocation\n434: - **WHEN** the output package flag is inspected\n435: - **THEN** it SHALL be `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n436: \n437: ---\n438: \n439: ## File Index\n440: \n441: ### Requirement: All generated files exist at expected paths\n442: \n443: The system SHALL produce the following file structure under `client-go/`.\n444: \n445: #### Scenario: Clientset files\n446: - **GIVEN** code generation completes\n447: - **THEN** the following files SHALL exist:\n448:   - `clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n449:   - `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n450:   - `clientset/versioned/scheme/doc.go`\n451:   - `clientset/versioned/fake/clientset_generated.go`\n452:   - `clientset/versioned/fake/register.go`\n453:   - `clientset/versioned/fake/doc.go`\n454: \n455: #### Scenario: Typed client files\n456: - **GIVEN** code generation completes\n457: - **THEN** the following files SHALL exist:\n458:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n459:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n460:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n461:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/generated_expansion.go`\n462:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n463:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_runtime_client.go`\n464:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_agentruntime.go`\n465:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_codeinterpreter.go`\n466:   - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/doc.go`\n467: \n468: #### Scenario: Informer files\n469: - **GIVEN** code generation completes\n470: - **THEN** the following files SHALL exist:\n471:   - `informers/externalversions/factory.go`\n472:   - `informers/externalversions/generic.go`\n473:   - `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go`\n474:   - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go`\n475:   - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n476:   - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n477:   - `informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go`\n478: \n479: #### Scenario: Lister files\n480: - **GIVEN** code generation completes\n481: - **THEN** the following files SHALL exist:\n482:   - `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n483:   - `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n484:   - `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go`\n485: \n486: ---\n487: \n488: ## File Changes\n489: \n490: | Action | File | Description |\n491: |--------|------|-------------|\n492: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | `Clientset`, `Interface`, constructors |\n493: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go` | Scheme / codecs for generated client |\n494: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/doc.go` | Doc |\n495: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/clientset_generated.go` | Fake clientset implementation |\n496: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/register.go` | Fake scheme wiring |\n497: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/doc.go` | Doc |\n498: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | `RuntimeV1alpha1Client`, `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` |\n499: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | `AgentRuntimeInterface`, typed REST client |\n500: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | `CodeInterpreterInterface`, typed REST client |\n501: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/generated_expansion.go` | Expansion interfaces |\n502: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | Doc |\n503: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_runtime_client.go` | Fake runtime group client |\n504: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_agentruntime.go` | Fake AgentRuntime client |\n505: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_codeinterpreter.go` | Fake CodeInterpreter client |\n506: | Create | `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/doc.go` | Doc |\n507: | Create | `client-go/informers/externalversions/factory.go` | `SharedInformerFactory`, options, lifecycle |\n508: | Create | `client-go/informers/externalversions/generic.go` | `GenericInformer`, `ForResource` |\n509: | Create | `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` | Group `runtime` informer accessor |\n510: | Create | `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | `v1alpha1` informer accessors |\n511: | Create | `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | AgentRuntime informer + constructor |\n512: | Create | `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | CodeInterpreter informer + constructor |\n513: | Create | `client-go/informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go` | Base factory interface + types |\n514: | Create | `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | `AgentRuntimeLister`, namespace lister |\n515: | Create | `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | `CodeInterpreterLister`, namespace lister |\n516: | Create | `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` | Lister expansion interfaces |\n\n(End of file - total 516 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `client-go`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** L\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Scope\n\nThis delta spec covers the generated Kubernetes client-go library for API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, module path `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`. It SHALL provide a typed Clientset, per-resource REST clients, SharedInformerFactory, Listers, and in-memory Fake clients for the `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` custom resources. All code SHALL be generated via `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh` using `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 with `--with-watch` flag.\n\n---\n\n## Clientset\n\n### Requirement: Interface contract\n\nThe system SHALL provide a `Clientset` implementing `Interface` with discovery and group accessor methods.","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775882519183,"end":1775882519198}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882520499,"sessionID":"ses_2852778a9ffeIT20W4PZTyOUe6","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad8c310001ChcdhYAc1S6f5I","messageID":"msg_d7ad8af25001Jay1msJBgRNTGZ","sessionID":"ses_2852778a9ffeIT20W4PZTyOUe6","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_f424fa8528444b8faabad4c1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成 — Design/设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n6: \n7: 本变更将 AgentCube 现有的手写 `client-go` 库替换为由 `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 自动生成的标准 Kubernetes 风格客户端库。当前手写实现中，`real.go` 的 `NewForConfig` 返回空 `Clientset{}`，Informer 使用空的 `ListWatch{}`，Lister 虽然实现了基于 `cache.Indexer` 的查询但缺少与 Informer 的联动。这些 stub 实现无法在真实 Kubernetes 集群中工作。\n8: \n9: 生成后的客户端库将为 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` CRD（API Group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`）提供：\n10: 1. **类型安全的 REST 客户端** — 通过 `rest.RESTClient` 与 Kubernetes API Server 通信，支持完整 CRUD + Watch + Patch + DeleteCollection\n11: 2. **SharedInformerFactory** — 事件驱动的缓存同步机制，支持 `Start`/`Shutdown`/`WaitForCacheSync` 生命周期和 `WithNamespace`/`WithTweakListOptions` 等选项\n12: 3. **Listers** — 基于 `cache.Indexer` 的只读缓存索引，提供 O(1) 按 key 查询和 O(n) 按 selector 遍历\n13: 4. **Fake Clientset** — 内存级测试替身，使用 `k8s.io/client-go/testing.Fake` 框架，支持 Action/Reactor 模式\n14: \n15: 所有代码由 `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh` 自动生成，不应手动修改（`Expansion` 接口除外）。\n16: \n17: ### 1.2 目录结构 (Directory Layout)\n18: \n19: **当前状态 (Before):**\n20: \n21: ```\n22: client-go/\n23: ├── clientset/\n24: │   ├── clientset.go              # Interface (仅 RuntimeV1alpha1(), 无 Discovery())\n25: │   ├── real.go                   # Clientset (stub: NewForConfig 返回空 Clientset{})\n26: │   ├── fake.go                   # FakeClientset (基于 ObjectStore, 非 testing.Fake)\n27: │   └── typed/runtime/v1alpha1/\n28: │       ├── interfaces.go         # AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface, RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n29: │       ├── client.go             # RuntimeV1alpha1Client (基于 ObjectStore)\n30: │       └── runtime_client.go     # ObjectStore + AgentRuntimeClient + CodeInterpreterClient (内存 CRUD)\n31: ├── informers/externalversions/\n32: │   ├── factory.go                # SharedInformerFactory (stub: Start/Shutdown 仅转发 realFactory)\n33: │   └── runtime/\n34: │       ├── interface.go          # Runtime group interface (stub)\n35: │       └── v1alpha1/interface.go # Informer interfaces (stub: 空 ListWatch{})\n36: └── listers/runtime/v1alpha1/\n37:     └── expansion_generated.go    # Lister interfaces + 实现 (唯一功能完整的部分)\n38: ```\n39: \n40: **目标状态 (After):**\n41: \n42: ```\n43: client-go/\n44: ├── clientset/\n45: │   └── versioned/\n46: │       ├── clientset.go                    # Clientset, Interface, 4 个构造函数\n47: │       ├── scheme/\n48: │       │   ├── register.go                 # Scheme, Codecs, ParameterCodec, AddToScheme\n49: │       │   └── doc.go                      # +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n50: │       ├── fake/\n51: │       │   ├── clientset_generated.go      # NewSimpleClientset, NewClientset\n52: │       │   ├── register.go                 # Fake scheme wiring\n53: │       │   └── doc.go\n54: │       └── typed/runtime/v1alpha1/\n55: │           ├── runtime_client.go           # RuntimeV1alpha1Client, RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n56: │           ├── agentruntime.go             # AgentRuntimeInterface, *agentRuntimes\n57: │           ├── codeinterpreter.go          # CodeInterpreterInterface, *codeInterpreters\n58: │           ├── generated_expansion.go      # AgentRuntimeExpansion, CodeInterpreterExpansion (空)\n59: │           ├── doc.go\n60: │           └── fake/\n61: │               ├── fake_runtime_client.go  # FakeRuntimeV1alpha1\n62: │               ├── fake_agentruntime.go    # FakeAgentRuntimes\n63: │               ├── fake_codeinterpreter.go # FakeCodeInterpreters\n64: │               └── doc.go\n65: ├── informers/externalversions/\n66: │   ├── factory.go                          # SharedInformerFactory, 构造函数, 选项, 生命周期\n67: │   ├── generic.go                          # GenericInformer, ForResource\n68: │   ├── internalinterfaces/\n69: │   │   └── factory_interfaces.go           # NewInformerFunc, SharedInformerFactory, TweakListOptionsFunc\n70: │   └── runtime/\n71: │       ├── interface.go                    # Group runtime informer accessor\n72: │       └── v1alpha1/\n73: │           ├── interface.go                # v1alpha1 informer accessors\n74: │           ├── agentruntime.go             # AgentRuntimeInformer + 构造函数\n75: │           └── codeinterpreter.go          # CodeInterpreterInformer + 构造函数\n76: └── listers/runtime/v1alpha1/\n77:     ├── agentruntime.go                     # AgentRuntimeLister, AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n78:     ├── codeinterpreter.go                  # CodeInterpreterLister, CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister\n79:     └── expansion_generated.go              # 四个空 Expansion 接口\n80: ```\n81: \n82: **迁移策略**: 生成代码将完全替换现有 `client-go/` 目录内容。现有手写代码的 `ObjectStore` 模式将被 `k8s.io/client-go/testing.Fake` 替代；stub Informer 将被真实的 `cache.SharedIndexInformer` 替代。接口签名保持兼容（`RuntimeV1alpha1()` 方法名不变），但返回类型从手写实现变为生成实现。\n83: \n84: ### 1.3 依赖关系 (Dependencies)\n85: \n86: ```\n87: AR-035 client-go 生成\n88:   ├── 前置依赖\n89:   │   ├── pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 类型定义      # AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter (+genclient marker)\n90:   │   ├── zz_generated.deepcopy.go                # DeepCopy 方法 (已由 deepcopy-gen 生成)\n91:   │   ├── k8s.io/code-generator v0.34.1           # 代码生成工具 (dev-only)\n92:   │   └── k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1                # REST 客户端, Discovery, Fake 基础\n93:   │\n94:   ├── 构建依赖\n95:   │   ├── k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1             # Scheme, Codec, meta 类型\n96:   │   ├── k8s.io/kube-openapi                       # 可选, 用于 openapi-gen\n97:   │   └── Go 1.22+                                # code-generator v0.34.1 最低要求\n98:   │\n99:   ├── 生成脚本\n100:   │   ├── hack/update-codegen.sh                  # 主生成脚本\n101:   │   ├── hack/boilerplate.go.txt                 # 文件头注释模板\n102:   │   └── Makefile (gen-client target)            # 构建入口\n103:   │\n104:   └── 消费者 (后续 AR)\n105:       ├── pkg/workloadmanager                     # 使用 client-go 操作 CRD\n106:       ├── pkg/agentd                              # 使用 Informer 监听资源变化\n107:       └── 外部 Go 消费者                           # 导入 github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go\n108: ```\n109: \n110: ### 1.4 代码生成管线\n111: \n112: ```\n113: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/          # 输入: 类型定义 + marker\n114:   ├── agent_type.go                 #   +genclient, +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n115:   ├── codeinterpreter_types.go      #   +genclient, +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n116:   ├── groupversion_info.go          #   SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme\n117:   └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go      #   预生成 (deepcopy-gen)\n118: \n119:        │\n120:        ▼\n121: hack/update-codegen.sh              # 生成脚本\n122:   ├── client-gen                    # → clientset/versioned/\n123:   ├── lister-gen                    # → listers/\n124:   ├── informer-gen                  # → informers/\n125:   └── deepcopy-gen                  # → pkg/apis/.../zz_generated.deepcopy.go (验证)\n126: \n127:        │\n128:        ▼\n129: client-go/                          # 输出: 生成的客户端库\n130:   ├── clientset/versioned/          #   Clientset, typed clients, fake, scheme\n131:   ├── informers/externalversions/   #   SharedInformerFactory, per-type informers\n132:   └── listers/runtime/v1alpha1/     #   Listers, namespace listers\n133: ```\n134: \n135: ---\n136: \n137: ## 2. 数据结构 (Data Structures)\n138: \n139: ### 2.1 输入类型定义\n140: \n141: 生成代码的输入为 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 中已定义的 CRD 类型。这些类型必须包含正确的 marker 注释：\n142: \n143: **AgentRuntime** (`agent_type.go`):\n144: ```go\n145: // +genclient\n146: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n147: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n148: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes\n149: type AgentRuntime struct {\n150:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n151:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n152:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n153:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n154: }\n155: \n156: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n157:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n158:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n159:     Items []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n160: }\n161: ```\n162: \n163: **CodeInterpreter** (`codeinterpreter_types.go`):\n164: ```go\n165: // +genclient\n166: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n167: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n168: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=codeinterpreters\n169: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n170:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n171:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n172:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n173:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n174: }\n175: \n176: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n177:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n178:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n179:     Items []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n180: }\n181: ```\n182: \n183: ### 2.2 生成接口层次\n184: \n185: ```\n186: versioned.Interface                          # Clientset 顶层接口\n187: ├── Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n188: └── RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n189: \n190: runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface     # 分组接口\n191: ├── RESTClient() rest.Interface\n192: ├── AgentRuntimes(namespace) AgentRuntimeInterface\n193: └── CodeInterpreters(namespace) CodeInterpreterInterface\n194: \n195: AgentRuntimeInterface                        # 资源接口 (+genclient 生成)\n196: ├── Create(ctx, *AgentRuntime, CreateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)\n197: ├── Update(ctx, *AgentRuntime, UpdateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)\n198: ├── UpdateStatus(ctx, *AgentRuntime, UpdateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)\n199: ├── Delete(ctx, name, DeleteOptions) error\n200: ├── DeleteCollection(ctx, DeleteOptions, ListOptions) error\n201: ├── Get(ctx, name, GetOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)\n202: ├── List(ctx, ListOptions) (*AgentRuntimeList, error)\n203: ├── Watch(ctx, ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n204: ├── Patch(ctx, name, PatchType, []byte, PatchOptions, ...string) (*AgentRuntime, error)\n205: └── AgentRuntimeExpansion                    # 空接口, 预留扩展\n206: \n207: informers.SharedInformerFactory              # Informer 工厂\n208: ├── internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory\n209: │   ├── Start(stopCh)\n210: │   └── InformerFor(obj, newFunc) SharedIndexInformer\n211: ├── Shutdown()\n212: ├── WaitForCacheSync(stopCh) map[reflect.Type]bool\n213: ├── ForResource(GVR) (GenericInformer, error)\n214: ├── InformerFor(obj, newFunc) SharedIndexInformer\n215: └── Runtime() externalversionsruntime.Interface\n216: \n217: AgentRuntimeInformer                         # 类型 Informer\n218: ├── Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n219: └── Lister() AgentRuntimeLister\n220: \n221: AgentRuntimeLister                           # 类型 Lister\n222: ├── List(selector) ([]*AgentRuntime, error)\n223: ├── AgentRuntimes(namespace) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n224: └── AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n225: \n226: AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister                  # 命名空间 Lister\n227: ├── List(selector) ([]*AgentRuntime, error)\n228: ├── Get(name) (*AgentRuntime, error)\n229: └── AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion\n230: ```\n231: \n232: ### 2.3 关键结构体\n233: \n234: **Clientset** (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`):\n235: ```go\n236: type Clientset struct {\n237:     *discovery.DiscoveryClient\n238:     runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client\n239: }\n240: ```\n241: \n242: **RuntimeV1alpha1Client** (`clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`):\n243: ```go\n244: type RuntimeV1alpha1Client struct {\n245:     restClient rest.Interface\n246: }\n247: ```\n248: \n249: **SharedInformerFactory** (`informers/externalversions/factory.go`):\n250: ```go\n251: type sharedInformerFactory struct {\n252:     client           versioned.Interface\n253:     defaultResync    time.Duration\n254:     customResync     map[reflect.Type]time.Duration\n255:     namespace        string\n256:     tweakListOptions internalinterfaces.TweakListOptionsFunc\n257:     lock             sync.Mutex\n258:     informers        map[reflect.Type]cache.SharedIndexInformer\n259:     startedInformers map[reflect.Type]bool\n260: }\n261: ```\n262: \n263: **Per-type Informer** (`informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`):\n264: ```go\n265: type agentRuntimeInformer struct {\n266:     factory          internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory\n267:     tweakListOptions internalinterfaces.TweakListOptionsFunc\n268:     namespace        string\n269: }\n270: ```\n271: \n272: **Lister** (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`):\n273: ```go\n274: type agentRuntimeLister struct {\n275:     indexer cache.Indexer\n276: }\n277: \n278: type agentRuntimeNamespaceLister struct {\n279:     indexer   cache.Indexer\n280:     namespace string\n281: }\n282: ```\n283: \n284: ### 2.4 数据流关系\n285: \n286: ```\n287: Kubernetes API Server\n288:        │\n289:        │ REST (HTTPS)\n290:        ▼\n291: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n292: │  RuntimeV1alpha1Client              │\n293: │  (rest.RESTClient)                  │\n294: │  - GroupVersion: runtime.../v1alpha1│\n295: │  - APIPath: /apis                   │\n296: │  - NegotiatedSerializer: scheme     │\n297: └──────────┬──────────────────────────┘\n298:            │\n299:            │ Create/Update/Get/List/Watch/Patch\n300:            ▼\n301: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n302: │  AgentRuntimeInterface              │\n303: │  CodeInterpreterInterface           │\n304: │  (typed REST operations)            │\n305: └─────────────────────────────────────┘\n306: \n307: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n308: │  SharedInformerFactory              │\n309: │  Start() → 启动所有 Informer         │\n310: │  WaitForCacheSync() → 等待同步完成   │\n311: └──────────┬──────────────────────────┘\n312:            │\n313:            │ 每个类型一个 Informer\n314:            ▼\n315: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n316: │  AgentRuntimeInformer               │\n317: │  - Informer(): SharedIndexInformer  │\n318: │    List + Watch → 本地缓存           │\n319: │  - Lister(): AgentRuntimeLister     │\n320: │    从缓存读取, 无网络请求             │\n321: └─────────────────────────────────────┘\n322: ```\n323: \n324: ---\n325: \n326: ## 3. API 契约 (API Contracts)\n327: \n328: ### 3.1 Clientset 构造函数\n329: \n330: | 函数 | 签名 | 行为 |\n331: |------|------|------|\n332: | `NewForConfig` | `func(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)` | 从 `rest.Config` 构建 Clientset；为每个 API group 创建 `rest.RESTClient`；失败返回 error |\n333: | `NewForConfigAndClient` | `func(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)` | 同 `NewForConfig`，但使用自定义 `http.Client` 作为传输层 |\n334: | `NewForConfigOrDie` | `func(c *rest.Config) *Clientset` | 同 `NewForConfig`，失败时 panic |\n335: | `New` | `func(c rest.Interface) *Clientset` | 从已配置的 `rest.Interface` 构建 Clientset（用于测试或自定义场景） |\n336: \n337: ### 3.2 Typed REST Client 行为\n338: \n339: **AgentRuntimeInterface** 和 **CodeInterpreterInterface** 的方法签名由 code-generator 根据类型定义自动生成，遵循 Kubernetes 标准约定：\n340: \n341: | 方法 | HTTP 方法 | URL 模式 | 说明 |\n342: |------|-----------|----------|------|\n343: | `Create` | POST | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}` | 创建资源 |\n344: | `Update` | PUT | `/apis/.../v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}/{name}` | 更新资源（全量替换） |\n345: | `UpdateStatus` | PUT | `/apis/.../v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}/{name}/status` | 仅更新 status 子资源 |\n346: | `Delete` | DELETE | `/apis/.../v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}/{name}` | 删除资源 |\n347: | `DeleteCollection` | DELETE | `/apis/.../v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}` | 批量删除（带 ListOptions 过滤） |\n348: | `Get` | GET | `/apis/.../v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}/{name}` | 获取单个资源 |\n349: | `List` | GET | `/apis/.../v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}` | 列出资源集合 |\n350: | `Watch` | GET | `/apis/.../v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}?watch=true` | 建立 Watch 流 |\n351: | `Patch` | PATCH | `/apis/.../v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/{resource}/{name}` | 部分更新 |\n352: \n353: **资源复数形式**:\n354: - `AgentRuntime` → `agentruntimes`\n355: - `CodeInterpreter` → `codeinterpreters`\n356: \n357: ### 3.3 Informer Factory 选项\n358: \n359: | 选项函数 | 签名 | 用途 |\n360: |----------|------|------|\n361: | `WithCustomResyncConfig` | `func(resync map[reflect.Type]time.Duration) SharedInformerOption` | 为不同类型设置不同的 resync 间隔 |\n362: | `WithTweakListOptions` | `func(tweak internalinterfaces.TweakListOptionsFunc) SharedInformerOption` | 修改每次 List/Watch 的 ListOptions |\n363: | `WithNamespace` | `func(namespace string) SharedInformerOption` | 限制 Informer 监听的命名空间 |\n364: | `WithTransform` | `func(transform cache.TransformFunc) SharedInformerOption` | 在对象存入缓存前进行转换 |\n365: \n366: ### 3.4 Fake Clientset 契约\n367: \n368: Fake Clientset 使用 `k8s.io/client-go/testing` 框架：\n369: \n370: ```go\n371: // 创建带初始对象的 Fake Clientset\n372: fakeClientset := fake.NewSimpleClientset(\n373:     &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n374:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"},\n375:     },\n376: )\n377: \n378: // 添加自定义 Reactor\n379: fakeClientset.PrependReactor(\"get\", \"agentruntimes\", func(action testing.Action) (bool, runtime.Object, error) {\n380:     // 自定义行为\n381:     return true, nil, apierrors.NewNotFound(v1alpha1.Resource(\"agentruntime\"), action.(testing.GetAction).GetName())\n382: })\n383: ```\n384: \n385: ### 3.5 与现有代码的兼容性\n386: \n387: | 现有接口 | 生成接口 | 兼容性 |\n388: |----------|----------|--------|\n389: | `Interface.RuntimeV1alpha1()` | `Interface.RuntimeV1alpha1()` | ✅ 签名兼容 |\n390: | `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface.AgentRuntimes(ns)` | `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface.AgentRuntimes(ns)` | ✅ 签名兼容 |\n391: | `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface.CodeInterpreters(ns)` | `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface.CodeInterpreters(ns)` | ✅ 签名兼容 |\n392: | `AgentRuntimeInterface` 方法集 | `AgentRuntimeInterface` 方法集 | ✅ 增加 `DeleteCollection` |\n393: | `SharedInformerFactory.Start()` | `SharedInformerFactory.Start(stopCh)` | ⚠️ 参数类型变化 (`<-chan struct{}`) |\n394: | `SharedInformerFactory.WaitForCacheSync()` | `SharedInformerFactory.WaitForCacheSync(stopCh)` | ⚠️ 返回值类型变化 (`map[reflect.Type]bool`) |\n395: | `FakeClientset` | `fake.NewSimpleClientset()` | ❌ 完全不同的 API |\n396: \n397: ---\n398: \n399: ## 4. 错误处理 (Error Handling)\n400: \n401: ### 4.1 错误来源分类\n402: \n403: | 错误类别 | 来源 | 典型错误类型 | 处理策略 |\n404: |----------|------|-------------|----------|\n405: | **配置错误** | `NewForConfig` 参数无效 | `rest.Config` 字段缺失 | 构造函数返回 error，调用方处理 |\n406: | **网络错误** | API Server 不可达 | `*url.Error`, `net.OpError` | 透传 error，调用方重试或降级 |\n407: | **API 错误** | API Server 返回非 2xx | `*apierrors.StatusError` | 使用 `apierrors.Is*` 辅助函数判断 |\n408: | **资源不存在** | Get/Delete 不存在的资源 | `apierrors.NewNotFound` | 调用方判断 `apierrors.IsNotFound(err)` |\n409: | **资源已存在** | Create 已存在的资源 | `apierrors.NewAlreadyExists` | 调用方判断 `apierrors.IsAlreadyExists(err)` |\n410: | **冲突** | Update 时 resourceVersion 不匹配 | `apierrors.NewConflict` | 调用方判断 `apierrors.IsConflict(err)`，重试 |\n411: | **验证失败** | 提交无效资源 | `apierrors.NewInvalid` | 调用方检查 `err.ErrStatus.Details.Causes` |\n412: \n413: ### 4.2 标准错误判断模式\n414: \n415: ```go\n416: // 资源不存在\n417: obj, err := client.AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Get(ctx, \"my-runtime\", metav1.GetOptions{})\n418: if apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n419:     // 资源不存在, 创建或跳过\n420: }\n421: \n422: // 资源已存在\n423: _, err = client.AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(ctx, runtime, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n424: if apierrors.IsAlreadyExists(err) {\n425:     // 已存在, Update 或跳过\n426: }\n427: \n428: // 冲突 (并发更新)\n429: _, err = client.AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Update(ctx, runtime, metav1.UpdateOptions{})\n430: if apierrors.IsConflict(err) {\n431:     // 重新 Get → 修改 → Update\n432: }\n433: ```\n434: \n435: ### 4.3 Informer 错误处理\n436: \n437: - **List 失败**: `Start()` 不会阻塞，错误通过 Informer 的 `WatchErrorHandler` 报告（默认 log）\n438: - **Watch 断开**: Informer 自动重试（指数退避），无需调用方干预\n439: - **缓存未就绪**: `WaitForCacheSync()` 返回 `false`，调用方应等待或报错\n440: - **对象类型不匹配**: `cache.ListAll` 返回类型断言错误，通常为编程错误\n441: \n442: ### 4.4 Fake Client 错误行为\n443: \n444: Fake Client 默认行为：\n445: - `Get` 不存在的资源 → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n446: - `Create` 已存在的资源 → `apierrors.NewAlreadyExists`\n447: - `Update` 不存在的资源 → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n448: - `Delete` 不存在的资源 → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n449: \n450: 可通过 `PrependReactor` 覆盖默认行为以模拟特定错误场景。\n451: \n452: ---\n453: \n454: ## 5. 测试策略 (Testing Strategy)\n455: \n456: ### 5.1 测试分层\n457: \n458: ```\n459: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n460: │  集成测试 (E2E)                                  │\n461: │  - 使用 envtest (k8s.io/client-go/tools/envtest) │\n462: │  - 启动真实 API Server (etcd + kube-apiserver)   │\n463: │  - 验证 Clientset + Informer + Lister 端到端行为  │\n464: ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n465: │  单元测试 (Fake Client)                          │\n466: │  - 使用 fake.NewSimpleClientset                  │\n467: │  - 验证 CRUD 操作的正确性                         │\n468: │  - 验证错误场景 (NotFound, Conflict, etc.)        │\n469: ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n470: │  生成代码验证                                    │\n471: │  - 验证生成的文件编译通过                         │\n472: │  - 验证接口签名符合预期                           │\n473: │  - 验证 Scheme 注册完整                          │\n474: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n475: ```\n476: \n477: ### 5.2 生成代码验证测试\n478: \n479: **编译验证**: `make gen-client` 后执行 `go build ./client-go/...`，确保所有生成的文件编译通过。\n480: \n481: **接口验证**: 使用接口实现检查确保生成的类型满足预期接口：\n482: \n483: ```go\n484: // 编译时接口检查\n485: var _ versioned.Interface = &clientset.Clientset{}\n486: var _ runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface = &clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1Client{}\n487: var _ runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInterface = &clientset.AgentRuntime{}\n488: var _ runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterInterface = &clientset.CodeInterpreter{}\n489: ```\n490: \n491: **Scheme 验证**: 验证所有类型已正确注册：\n492: \n493: ```go\n494: func TestSchemeRegistration(t *testing.T) {\n495:     scheme := scheme.Scheme\n496:     gvk := schema.GroupVersionKind{\n497:         Group:   \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n498:         Version: \"v1alpha1\",\n499:         Kind:    \"AgentRuntime\",\n500:     }\n501:     obj, err := scheme.New(gvk)\n502:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n503:     assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}, obj)\n504: }\n505: ```\n506: \n507: ### 5.3 Fake Client 单元测试\n508: \n509: 测试场景覆盖：\n510: \n511: | 场景 | 测试内容 |\n512: |------|----------|\n513: | CRUD 生命周期 | Create → Get → Update → List → Delete → Get(NotFound) |\n514: | UpdateStatus | 仅修改 status 字段，spec 不变 |\n515: | DeleteCollection | 创建多个资源，DeleteCollection 后 List 为空 |\n516: | Watch | 创建资源后 Watch 收到 ADDED 事件 |\n517: | Patch | Patch 部分字段后 Get 验证 |\n518: | 错误场景 | Get 不存在 → IsNotFound, Create 已存在 → IsAlreadyExists |\n519: | 命名空间隔离 | 不同 namespace 的资源互不影响 |\n520: \n521: ### 5.4 Informer 集成测试\n522: \n523: 使用 `envtest` 启动真实 API Server：\n524: \n525: ```go\n526: func TestInformerSync(t *testing.T) {\n527:     // 启动 envtest\n528:     cfg, teardown := envtest.Setup(t)\n529:     defer teardown()\n530: \n531:     // 创建 Clientset\n532:     cs, _ := versioned.NewForConfig(cfg)\n533: \n534:     // 创建 Informer Factory\n535:     factory := informers.NewSharedInformerFactory(cs, 30*time.Second)\n536:     informer := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()\n537: \n538:     // 启动 Informer\n539:     stopCh := make(chan struct{})\n540:     factory.Start(stopCh)\n541:     synced := factory.WaitForCacheSync(stopCh)\n542:     assert.True(t, synced[reflect.TypeOf(&v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{})])\n543: \n544:     // 创建资源, 验证 Informer 缓存同步\n545:     cs.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(ctx, runtime, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n546:     time.Sleep(1 * time.Second)\n547: \n548:     lister := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Lister()\n549:     items, _ := lister.List(labels.Everything())\n550:     assert.Len(t, items, 1)\n551: }\n552: ```\n553: \n554: ### 5.5 回归测试\n555: \n556: 每次 `make gen-client` 后运行：\n557: \n558: ```bash\n559: make gen-client && go build ./client-go/... && go test ./client-go/...\n560: ```\n561: \n562: 确保生成代码：\n563: 1. 编译通过\n564: 2. 所有现有测试通过（使用新的 Fake Clientset）\n565: 3. 接口签名与 delta-spec.md 中的场景一致\n566: \n567: ---\n568: \n569: ## 6. 实现步骤 (Implementation Steps)\n570: \n571: ### Phase 1: 生成基础设施 (T-001)\n572: \n573: **目标**: 建立代码生成管线，确保 `make gen-client` 可运行\n574: \n575: 1. 添加 `hack/update-codegen.sh` 脚本\n576:    - 使用 `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1\n577:    - 调用 `client-gen`, `lister-gen`, `informer-gen`, `deepcopy-gen`\n578:    - 设置 `--with-watch` 标志\n579:    - 输出包路径: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n580: \n581: 2. 添加 `hack/boilerplate.go.txt` 文件头模板\n582: \n583: 3. 在 `Makefile` 中添加 `gen-client` target\n584: \n585: 4. 确保 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 类型定义包含正确的 marker:\n586:    - `// +genclient` (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\n587:    - `// +kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n588:    - `doc.go` 包含 `// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` 和 `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n589: \n590: 5. 运行 `make gen-client` 验证生成成功\n591: \n592: **验收**: `make gen-client` 执行成功，`client-go/` 目录下生成所有预期文件\n593: \n594: ### Phase 2: Clientset 和 Typed Client (T-002)\n595: \n596: **目标**: 生成 Clientset 和 Typed REST Client\n597: \n598: 生成文件:\n599: - `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` — Clientset, Interface, 4 个构造函数\n600: - `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go` — Scheme, Codecs, ParameterCodec\n601: - `clientset/versioned/scheme/doc.go`\n602: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` — RuntimeV1alpha1Client\n603: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` — AgentRuntimeInterface\n604: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` — CodeInterpreterInterface\n605: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/generated_expansion.go` — 空 Expansion 接口\n606: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n607: \n608: **验收**: \n609: - `go build ./client-go/clientset/...` 编译通过\n610: - `NewForConfig` 返回的 Clientset 可调用 `RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").List(ctx, metav1.ListOptions{})`\n611: \n612: ### Phase 3: Fake Clients (T-003)\n613: \n614: **目标**: 生成 Fake Clientset 和 Fake Typed Clients\n615: \n616: 生成文件:\n617: - `clientset/versioned/fake/clientset_generated.go` — NewSimpleClientset, NewClientset\n618: - `clientset/versioned/fake/register.go` — Fake scheme wiring\n619: - `clientset/versioned/fake/doc.go`\n620: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_runtime_client.go`\n621: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_agentruntime.go`\n622: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_codeinterpreter.go`\n623: - `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/doc.go`\n624: \n625: **验收**:\n626: - `fake.NewSimpleClientset()` 返回的 Clientset 实现 `versioned.Interface`\n627: - Fake CRUD 操作行为正确 (Create/Get/Update/Delete/List)\n628: - 错误场景正确 (NotFound, AlreadyExists)\n629: \n630: ### Phase 4: Informer Factory (T-004)\n631: \n632: **目标**: 生成 SharedInformerFactory 和 Per-type Informers\n633: \n634: 生成文件:\n635: - `informers/externalversions/factory.go` — SharedInformerFactory\n636: - `informers/externalversions/generic.go` — GenericInformer, ForResource\n637: - `informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go` — 基础接口\n638: - `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` — Group accessor\n639: - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` — Version accessor\n640: - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` — AgentRuntimeInformer\n641: - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` — CodeInterpreterInformer\n642: \n643: **验收**:\n644: - `NewSharedInformerFactory(cs, 30*time.Second)` 返回工厂\n645: - `factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()` 返回 SharedIndexInformer\n646: - `factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Lister()` 返回 AgentRuntimeLister\n647: - `ForResource(GVR)` 正确路由到对应 Informer\n648: \n649: ### Phase 5: Listers (T-005)\n650: \n651: **目标**: 生成 Listers 和 Namespace Listers\n652: \n653: 生成文件:\n654: - `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` — AgentRuntimeLister, AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n655: - `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` — CodeInterpreterLister, CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister\n656: - `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` — 四个空 Expansion 接口\n657: \n658: **验收**:\n659: - `NewAgentRuntimeLister(indexer)` 返回 Lister\n660: - `lister.List(labels.Everything())` 返回所有资源\n661: - `lister.AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Get(\"name\")` 返回命名空间内的资源\n662: \n663: ### Phase 6: 迁移和清理 (T-006)\n664: \n665: **目标**: 删除手写代码，更新消费者使用生成的客户端\n666: \n667: 1. 删除现有手写 `client-go/` 目录内容\n668: 2. 更新所有导入路径:\n669:    - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset` → `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned`\n670:    - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/informers/...` → 新路径\n671:    - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/listers/...` → 新路径\n672: 3. 更新使用 FakeClientset 的测试代码，改用 `fake.NewSimpleClientset()`\n673: 4. 运行 `make test` 确保所有测试通过\n674: \n675: **验收**:\n676: - `go build ./...` 编译通过\n677: - `make test` 所有测试通过\n678: - `make lint` 无错误\n679: \n680: ### Phase 7: 文档和验证 (T-007)\n681: \n682: **目标**: 更新文档，验证生成代码质量\n683: \n684: 1. 更新 `deployment/client-go.md` 反映生成代码结构\n685: 2. 在 `README` 或文档中添加 client-go 使用说明\n686: 3. 运行 `go vet ./client-go/...` 验证代码质量\n687: 4. 验证生成的文件包含正确的文件头注释\n688: \n689: **验收**:\n690: - 文档更新完成\n691: - `go vet` 无警告\n692: - 生成代码符合 Kubernetes 代码规范\n693: \n694: ---\n695: \n696: ## 7. 后续变更 (Follow-up Changes)\n697: \n698: ### 7.1 依赖关系\n699: \n700: ```\n701: T-001 (生成基础设施)\n702:   └── T-002 (Clientset + Typed Client)\n703:         ├── T-003 (Fake Clients)          ← 可与 T-004 并行\n704:         └── T-004 (Informer Factory)\n705:               └── T-005 (Listers)         ← 可与 T-003 并行\n706:                     └── T-006 (迁移清理)\n707:                           └── T-007 (文档验证)\n708: ```\n709: \n710: ### 7.2 可并行组\n711: \n712: | 组 | 任务 | 前置条件 |\n713: |----|------|----------|\n714: | G1 | T-003 (Fake Clients), T-004 (Informer Factory) | T-002 完成 |\n715: | G2 | T-005 (Listers) | T-004 完成 |\n716: \n717: ### 7.3 后续可能的变更\n718: \n719: | 变更 | 描述 | 依赖 |\n720: |------|------|------|\n721: | **多 API Group 支持** | 为其他 API Group (如 `agents/v1alpha1`) 生成客户端 | AR-035 完成 |\n722: | **自定义 Informer 扩展** | 在 Expansion 接口中添加自定义方法 | AR-035 完成 |\n723: | **Controller-runtime 集成** | 使用生成的 client-go 构建控制器 | AR-035 完成 |\n724: | **客户端版本升级** | 升级 code-generator 到新版本 | AR-035 完成 |\n725: \n726: ### 7.4 已知限制\n727: \n728: 1. **生成代码不可手动修改**: 任何自定义逻辑必须通过 `Expansion` 接口注入\n729: 2. **单 API Group**: 当前仅生成 `runtime/v1alpha1`，其他 Group 需额外配置\n730: 3. **无自定义验证**: 生成代码不包含业务逻辑验证，由 API Server Webhook 处理\n731: 4. **Informer 全量同步**: 首次启动时需 List 全部资源，大量资源时初始同步较慢\n\n(End of file - total 731 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成 — Design/设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n\n### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n\n本变更将 AgentCube 现有的手写 `client-go` 库替换为由 `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 自动生成的标准 Kubernetes 风格客户端库。当前手写实现中，`real.go` 的 `NewForConfig` 返回空 `Clientset{}`，Informer 使用空的 `ListWatch{}`，Lister 虽然实现了基于 `cache.Indexer` 的查询但缺少与 Informer 的联动。这些 stub 实现无法在真实 Kubernetes 集群中工作。\n\n生成后的客户端库将为 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` CRD（API Group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`）提供：\n1. **类型安全的 REST 客户端** — 通过 `rest.RESTClient` 与 Kubernetes API Server 通信，支持完整 CRUD + Watch + Patch + DeleteCollection\n2. **SharedInformerFactory** — 事件驱动的缓存同步机制，支持 `Start`/`Shutdown`/`WaitForCacheSync` 生命周期和 `WithNamespace`/`WithTweakListOptions` 等选项\n3. **Listers** — 基于 `cache.Indexer` 的只读缓存索引，提供 O(1) 按 key 查询和 O(n) 按 selector 遍历\n4. **Fake Clientset** — 内存级测试替身，使用 `k8s.io/client-go/testing.Fake` 框架，支持 Action/Reactor 模式\n\n所有代码由 `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh` 自动生成，不应手动修改（`Expansion` 接口除外）。\n\n### 1.2 目录结构 (Directory Layout)\n\n**当前状态 (Before):**\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/design.md","time":{"start":1775882520482,"end":1775882520496}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882521796,"sessionID":"ses_2852778a9ffeIT20W4PZTyOUe6","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad8c858001oaaMLe2OBoem89","messageID":"msg_d7ad8af25001Jay1msJBgRNTGZ","sessionID":"ses_2852778a9ffeIT20W4PZTyOUe6","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_a7efe203bb9f4f7ba10871d0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** client-go\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** L\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-035/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-035/design.md`, `changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md`\n8: > **Dependency:** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` types with `+genclient` markers (already present), `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (already present)\n9: \n10: ---\n11: \n12: ## T-001: 生成基础设施 — hack/update-codegen.sh + Makefile gen-client\n13: \n14: - [ ] Create `hack/boilerplate.go.txt` with standard Apache 2.0 header template\n15: - [ ] Create `hack/update-codegen.sh` script that:\n16:   - [ ] Uses `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 (downloaded via `go run k8s.io/code-generator/cmd/...` or `go install`)\n17:   - [ ] Runs `client-gen` → outputs to `client-go/clientset/versioned/`\n18:   - [ ] Runs `lister-gen` → outputs to `client-go/listers/`\n19:   - [ ] Runs `informer-gen` → outputs to `client-go/informers/`\n20:   - [ ] Uses `--with-watch` flag on all generators\n21:   - [ ] Sets `--output-package=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n22:   - [ ] Sets `--input-base=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis` and `--input=runtime/v1alpha1`\n23:   - [ ] Sets `--go-header-file=hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n24:   - [ ] Is idempotent (can be re-run safely)\n25: - [ ] Add `gen-client` target to `Makefile` that invokes `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n26: - [ ] Add `gen-client` to `.PHONY` declaration\n27: - [ ] Verify `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` has `// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` and `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n28: - [ ] Verify `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` types have `// +genclient` marker\n29: - [ ] Run `make gen-client` and verify it completes without error\n30: - [ ] Verify all 26 expected files are generated (see File Index in delta-spec.md)\n31: \n32: **验收**:\n33: ```bash\n34: make gen-client\n35: go build ./client-go/...\n36: ```\n37: No compilation errors; all expected files exist under `client-go/`.\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ## T-002: Clientset 和 Typed REST Client 生成验证\n42: \n43: > Generated by T-001; this task verifies and validates the output.\n44: \n45: ### Clientset (`client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\n46: - [ ] `Interface` declares `Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface` and `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n47: - [ ] `Clientset` struct embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`\n48: - [ ] `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)` creates clientset from `rest.Config`\n49: - [ ] `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)` uses custom HTTP client\n50: - [ ] `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset` panics on invalid config\n51: - [ ] `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset` creates from pre-configured `rest.Interface`\n52: \n53: ### Scheme (`client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`)\n54: - [ ] `Scheme`, `Codecs`, `ParameterCodec` are package-level variables\n55: - [ ] `AddToScheme` registers `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n56: \n57: ### Typed Client (`client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n58: - [ ] `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` declares `RESTClient() rest.Interface`, `AgentRuntimesGetter`, `CodeInterpretersGetter`\n59: - [ ] `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` implements `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` with `rest.Interface`\n60: - [ ] `AgentRuntimesGetter` declares `AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface`\n61: - [ ] `CodeInterpretersGetter` declares `CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface`\n62: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeInterface` has all 9 CRUD methods: Create, Update, UpdateStatus, Delete, DeleteCollection, Get, List, Watch, Patch\n63: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterInterface` has all 9 CRUD methods with `CodeInterpreter` types\n64: - [ ] `AgentRuntime` resource plural is `agentruntimes`\n65: - [ ] `CodeInterpreter` resource plural is `codeinterpreters`\n66: - [ ] `generated_expansion.go` has empty `AgentRuntimeExpansion` and `CodeInterpreterExpansion` interfaces\n67: - [ ] `GroupVersion` is `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, `APIPath` is `/apis`\n68: \n69: ### Build verification\n70: - [ ] `go build ./client-go/clientset/...` compiles without errors\n71: - [ ] Compile-time interface check: `var _ versioned.Interface = &clientset.Clientset{}`\n72: - [ ] Compile-time interface check: `var _ runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface = &clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1Client{}`\n73: - [ ] Compile-time interface check: `var _ runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInterface = &clientset.AgentRuntime{}`\n74: - [ ] Compile-time interface check: `var _ runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterInterface = &clientset.CodeInterpreter{}`\n75: \n76: **验收**:\n77: ```bash\n78: go build ./client-go/clientset/...\n79: ```\n80: \n81: ---\n82: \n83: ## T-003: Fake Clients 生成验证\n84: \n85: > Generated by T-001; this task verifies and validates the fake client output.\n86: \n87: ### Fake Typed Clients (`client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/`)\n88: - [ ] `FakeRuntimeV1alpha1` embeds `*testing.Fake` and implements `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n89: - [ ] `FakeAgentRuntimes` implements `AgentRuntimeInterface` using `*testing.Fake` actions\n90: - [ ] `FakeCodeInterpreters` implements `CodeInterpreterInterface` using `*testing.Fake` actions\n91: \n92: ### Fake Clientset (`client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/`)\n93: - [ ] `NewSimpleClientset(objects ...runtime.Object) *Clientset` creates fake clientset with initial objects\n94: - [ ] `NewClientset(client *restclient.RESTClient, objects ...runtime.Object) *Clientset` with custom REST client\n95: - [ ] Fake `Clientset` implements `versioned.Interface`\n96: - [ ] `fake/register.go` wires same scheme as real clientset\n97: \n98: ### Fake behavior verification\n99: - [ ] `Get` non-existent resource → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n100: - [ ] `Create` existing resource → `apierrors.NewAlreadyExists`\n101: - [ ] `Update` non-existent resource → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n102: - [ ] `Delete` non-existent resource → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n103: - [ ] `PrependReactor` can override default behavior\n104: \n105: **验收**:\n106: ```bash\n107: go build ./client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/...\n108: go build ./client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/...\n109: ```\n110: \n111: ---\n112: \n113: ## T-004: Informer Factory 生成验证\n114: \n115: > Generated by T-001; this task verifies and validates the informer output.\n116: \n117: ### SharedInformerFactory (`informers/externalversions/factory.go`)\n118: - [ ] `SharedInformerFactory` interface embeds `internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory`\n119: - [ ] Declares `Start(stopCh <-chan struct{})`, `Shutdown()`, `WaitForCacheSync(stopCh) map[reflect.Type]bool`\n120: - [ ] Declares `ForResource(GVR) (GenericInformer, error)`, `InformerFor(obj, newFunc)`, `Runtime()`\n121: - [ ] `NewSharedInformerFactory(client, defaultResync)` constructor\n122: - [ ] `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(client, defaultResync, options...)` constructor\n123: - [ ] Options: `WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`\n124: \n125: ### Generic informer (`informers/externalversions/generic.go`)\n126: - [ ] `GenericInformer` wraps `SharedIndexInformer` with `Informer()` and `Lister()` methods\n127: - [ ] `ForResource(agentruntimes GVR)` → returns `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()`\n128: - [ ] `ForResource(codeinterpreters GVR)` → returns `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters().Informer()`\n129: - [ ] `ForResource(unknown GVR)` → returns `(nil, error)`\n130: \n131: ### internalinterfaces (`informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go`)\n132: - [ ] `NewInformerFunc` = `func(versioned.Interface, time.Duration) cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n133: - [ ] `SharedInformerFactory` declares `Start(stopCh <-chan struct{})` and `InformerFor(obj, newFunc)`\n134: - [ ] `TweakListOptionsFunc` = `func(*metav1.ListOptions)`\n135: \n136: ### Per-type informers (`informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n137: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeInformer` declares `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() AgentRuntimeLister`\n138: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterInformer` declares `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() CodeInterpreterLister`\n139: - [ ] `NewAgentRuntimeInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers)` returns `cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n140: - [ ] `NewFilteredAgentRuntimeInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers, tweakListOptions)` with filtered list options\n141: - [ ] `NewCodeInterpreterInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers)` returns `cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n142: - [ ] `NewFilteredCodeInterpreterInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers, tweakListOptions)` with filtered list options\n143: - [ ] Informers use real `cache.ListWatch` with List/Watch functions (not empty stubs)\n144: \n145: ### Group/version accessors\n146: - [ ] `Runtime()` returns `externalversionsruntime.Interface` with `V1alpha1()` method\n147: - [ ] `V1alpha1()` returns interface with `AgentRuntimes()` and `CodeInterpreters()` accessors\n148: \n149: **验收**:\n150: ```bash\n151: go build ./client-go/informers/...\n152: ```\n153: \n154: ---\n155: \n156: ## T-005: Listers 生成验证\n157: \n158: > Generated by T-001; this task verifies and validates the lister output.\n159: \n160: ### AgentRuntime Lister (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`)\n161: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeLister` declares `List(selector) ([]*AgentRuntime, error)`, `AgentRuntimes(namespace) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister`, `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion`\n162: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` declares `List(selector) ([]*AgentRuntime, error)`, `Get(name) (*AgentRuntime, error)`, `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion`\n163: - [ ] `NewAgentRuntimeLister(indexer)` uses `Resource(\"agentruntime\").GroupResource()` for error reporting\n164: \n165: ### CodeInterpreter Lister (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`)\n166: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterLister` declares `List`, `CodeInterpreters(namespace) CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister`, `CodeInterpreterListerExpansion`\n167: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` declares `List`, `Get`, `CodeInterpreterNamespaceListerExpansion`\n168: - [ ] `NewCodeInterpreterLister(indexer)` uses `Resource(\"codeinterpreter\").GroupResource()` for error reporting\n169: \n170: ### Expansion interfaces (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go`)\n171: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion` is empty interface\n172: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion` is empty interface\n173: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterListerExpansion` is empty interface\n174: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterNamespaceListerExpansion` is empty interface\n175: \n176: **验收**:\n177: ```bash\n178: go build ./client-go/listers/...\n179: ```\n180: \n181: ---\n182: \n183: ## T-006: 迁移 — 删除手写代码 + 更新消费者导入路径\n184: \n185: ### 删除手写代码\n186: - [ ] Delete `client-go/clientset/clientset.go` (old hand-written Interface)\n187: - [ ] Delete `client-go/clientset/real.go` (old stub Clientset)\n188: - [ ] Delete `client-go/clientset/fake.go` (old ObjectStore-based FakeClientset)\n189: - [ ] Delete `client-go/clientset/typed/` (old typed clients backed by ObjectStore)\n190: - [ ] Delete `client-go/informers/externalversi